Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:59.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115595,119557}It's been stolen!\NA picture more valuable than my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122685,124312}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:11.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130693,131819}Detective Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131819,132987}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:19.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137158,139410}You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:31.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148711,151881}I'll definitely get some evidence\Non you today, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:41.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156469,161224}Ohh! Not the painting that I stole!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161224,162266}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163059,164394}Oops. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164394,165311}Detective Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:46.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165728,166813}This picture…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:54.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168398,174153}It's the painting “Evening Primrose”,\Nstolen from the city museum last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174445,177281}Ah. It's… oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:58.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177573,178449}Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178449,180284}This is also a missing painting,\Nstolen two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:05.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181452,185289}Well! What is this all about?!\NShall we hear your explanation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:12.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191170,192004}Chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195466,197218}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201431,202765}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:32.44,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:207645,212442}The Cutest Little Thief!\NShe'll Steal Your Heart.{NOTE:登場！キュートな大泥棒！？\\Nあなたのハート盗みます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215361,217029}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:39.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218698,219657}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222201,223745}Good morning, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225705,226748}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228499,229417}Hey! Have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229417,231127}She appeared again last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231127,232462}Yes, she did, she did!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232462,236215}This time it was a mansion in Ward 16.\NMeimi, did you hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:00.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236716,240136}You're talking as if\Na strange ghost appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240136,242805}Are you talking about St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:07.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243806,247477}Her ponytail flutters in the wind\Nas she steals only from the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:11.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247477,251397}Because of her classy figure\Npeople call her St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251397,253775}But no one knows her true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:17.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253775,257487}Her tactful capers\Nhave never failed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257487,259363}She's as lightfooted as the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259363,261240}She's just wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263785,266746}And just what's so\Nwonderful about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:30.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267455,270208}Saint Tail or Sacred Tail,\Nwhichever it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271209,273377}A thief is a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:37.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273377,277215}How sickening,\Nto call her “wonderful”.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:41.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277590,281928}But I bet you'd like\Nto meet her, too, Asuka, Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:45.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281928,285431}No way! St. Tail is a mature lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285431,287558}She wouldn't even look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287558,289185}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289769,293689}Shut up! A pest like her!\NThis is what she looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294315,295650}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:58.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295650,298653}You know what kind\Nof person St. Tail is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299445,301989}These are her crimes for\Njust the past month…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:07.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301989,307620}Seven jewel robberies and\Ntwo stolen paintings, ten thefts total.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:12.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308204,312083}My suspicion is that it's all\Nbecause of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:16.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313084,316587}That's odd… I don't remember\Ntaking any jewels…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:17.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316587,317964}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:21.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317964,321050}Anyhow, Detective Asuka keeps\Nslipping up again and again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321050,323553}How can we believe\Nanything his son says?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:28.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323553,328015}Don't lump me in with my father!\NI'll be the one who catches St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:33.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329767,333229}St. Tail wouldn't be so cool\Nif somebody like you could catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333229,334230}What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334230,335106}What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336732,338109}Don't stop me, Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338109,339902}I'm not Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:43.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342738,343489}Seira…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:48.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344657,348286}Miss Haneoka, Mr. Asuka!\NThe two of you just stay right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348286,349495}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382111,384989}Excuse me, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:25.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384989,385781}Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:31.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387992,391954}Sister-in-training Seira.\NColdhearted Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:37.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391954,397251}Coldhearted is much too cruel.\NIt is all the teachings of our Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398294,400755}You passed a girl on your way in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:46.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402673,406802}Her name is Saori.\NShe came to ask God for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406802,408387}Such a young girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:59.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410681,419190}Her grandfather is a jewelry appraiser.\NOne day, he was brought two sapphires.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:06.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419899,426364}One of them was the “Blue Meteorite”,\Na very unique and expensive gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:09.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426364,429784}As a precaution against theft\Nthe owners had made a fake duplicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:13.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429784,433120}But the duplicate was so well made,\Nthat the gems got mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:17.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433120,437249}They couldn't tell which\Nwas the real “Blue Meteorite”.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:20.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437249,440461}That's why the dealer, Umido,\Nasked her grandfather for the appraisal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440461,442964}How does God\Nfit into a situation like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:27.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442964,447301}That's not the problem.\NNow the grandfather is asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447301,448803}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:39.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452223,459313}He was taken in\Nby the gem's beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:45.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461190,465277}He lied to Umido, telling him that\Nthe fake gem was the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:51.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465695,471033}Then he bought the other gem,\Nthe real one, at a cheap price.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:01.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477665,481961}That's fraud. He's a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481961,484880}Anyone can make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:09.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485673,489760}But a good human being regrets what\Nhe's done and tries to correct it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489760,492096}And today, we're going to be\Nof assistance with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492847,494390}Assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:21.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495266,501564}Thinking it was real, Umido sold the\Nfake “Blue Meteorite” to a rich woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501564,503232}So what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503232,505693}How do you think we should go\Nabout making things right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507737,511866}Well, I think switching the real gem\Nthat Saori's grandfather has
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511866,514201}with the fake gem that was sold\Nshould do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514201,515578}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518289,520082}The real gem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523502,526797}It's time for you to make\Nyour appearance, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533220,535264}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:56.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535723,536724}Welcome home, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536724,538017}Welcome home, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538017,539351}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539351,540895}Dinner will be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:06.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542146,546442}How's that! It's my new magic trick!\NBeautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:11.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546984,551739}Papa, you've got the hands of a wizard.\NI love it! The next show will be a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553240,555951}The two of you are making\Na mess of the room again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:20.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555951,560331}What's wrong with it? Meimi, you're\Ngoing to take after me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:25.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561248,565795}Who decided that? Meimi's going to take\Nafter her mother, aren't you Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:26.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565795,566796}Ah… sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566796,569882}You've gotta be joking!\NYour previous occupation was…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570508,572885}You're the one that took\None look at me and fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573260,575387}I'm getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:42.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578516,582353}It's time to get to work.\NI've got to help people in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:11.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608170,611257}Oh Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616220,617263}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619557,620933}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622810,624145}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:44.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640452,644248}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676071,678699}This must be where\Nshe keeps the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:23.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680576,683871}That's strange… why is it open?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:27.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686540,687374}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693672,696508}It's been stolen!\NThe “Blue Meteorite”!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696508,697301}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697301,698385}It's a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698385,699595}Better get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723619,725079}Kaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737299,738550}Did it go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738550,739051}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742471,744014}This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:29.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744598,749645}We steal back the gems that we sell\Nand then resell them to another sucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750187,752273}There are no rules in making money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754775,756277}That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:37.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756277,757778}Absolutely unforgivable!
Comment: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:37.77,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:757778,757778}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:43.78,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:763784,763784}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:48.78,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:768789,768789}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:57.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771000,777214}Meimi… you can't! It's dangerous.\NAnd I don't have information on Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:01.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777673,781927}Don't worry, nothing's impossible\Nfor St. Tail! I'll get through somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789601,792021}First, let's check out\Nthe houses of the wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:16.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792813,796567}Then overlap that with the locations\Nof unsolved crimes for the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:22.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798527,802906}So her next victim is…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803240,804366}Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805117,807870}St. Tail!\NI won't let you get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821967,824928}The alarm went off,\Nso we came over to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824928,826347}What's happened, Mr. Kaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:51.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827264,831810}Actually, a kid got himself caught\Nin our alarm system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:57.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832561,837191}At this hour? Who's the little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838609,839485}Hey! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844073,845199}Son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:05.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845199,845949}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:12.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846492,852164}Detective Asuka's son, is it?\NWell, how rude of me. Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:13.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852623,853916}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854875,857628}Hey, son, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858295,860047}St. Tail is coming here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:20.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860047,860839}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:25.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860839,865803}In the past month, this is the only place\Nthat hasn't been hit by a theft. So…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865803,868180}Leave this to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:31.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868180,871725}You can't catch St. Tail,\Nso I'm doing it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:34.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871725,874603}I've got other things to do\Nthan chase St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874603,876313}I'm very sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:43.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:877689,883862}I'd like to meet this St. Tail, myself.\NI hear she's a great thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884405,885322}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885739,886824}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893705,896083}It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896792,897960}What happened to the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:58.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897960,898794}They won't turn on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898794,900546}– Open the windows!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904883,906009}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906009,907094}What the…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941462,942796}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:48.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945716,948260}I'll just exchange the fake\None for the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:13.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971116,973785}May the blessings of God be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984004,985756}So, that's what this was all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987549,989218}Asuka, Jr.…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993805,995224}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:41.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996099,1001188}Well, how ingenious you are.\NStealing back the gems that you sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:46.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001605,1006652}How dare you call me a thief!\NWhat evidence do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:50.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007069,1010197}The evidence are\Nthese jewels, Mr. Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:53.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010197,1013700}These are all the jewels that\Nwere stolen in the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014326,1015953}St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:00.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017079,1020290}She always has a valid\Nreason for her capers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020290,1022584}St. Tail is not a crook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025003,1026588}That man…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027172,1029591}Mr. Kaido, the real crook is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:10.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029591,1030884}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030884,1032678}You won't be rattling on for long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046900,1049736}St. Tail, you're not\Ngetting away either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051071,1052739}Now I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053240,1054241}{\i1}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:39.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056201,1059705}{\i1}Oh, no!\NDon't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:55.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072593,1075262}St. Tail, don't be a coward!\NCome down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077764,1079766}Wait! Challenge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:04.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081435,1084229}At least send me a warning\Nthe next time you plan to appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086023,1087899}Don't forget to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089067,1090652}{\i1}That was a bit fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:26.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105792,1106835}Detective Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109838,1111173}These are…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:31.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111173,1111798}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:36.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112549,1116553}Aren't these all the stolen jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:45.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118221,1125520}{\i1}St. Tail… She seems to be\Nabout the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128607,1130525}I touched her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:06.20,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1143705,1146208}Take care of your grandfather
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:06.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144247,1146208}Take care of your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163308,1166937}I present this award of appreciation\Nfor the good deed you've performed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166937,1168188}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:39.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172484,1179616}And this one request, would you help us\Nin the arrest of St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:45.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183286,1185497}This is an official\Ninvestigation badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:49.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185497,1189543}Showing this will get\Nyou in anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:54.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190544,1194840}We definitely want to utilize your expertise\Nand knowledge in the St. Tail case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:57.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194840,1197342}Of course, with the cooperation\Nof the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197342,1198009}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:04.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200011,1204474}Today, Saori came to church\Nto express her thanks to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:10.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205100,1210439}They returned the jewels to their owners.\NI guess that's the end of the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:13.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211690,1213900}Then I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:17.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214484,1217154}See you tomorrow!\NBye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:22.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221074,1222659}Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223118,1224911}I heard you got an award.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:30.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224911,1230333}Yep! And next time,\NI'm gonna get that St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230876,1233837}Well, anyway…\Nhang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234463,1236339}Sure. Just watch me.
